snippet: In his third career start, Everett Golson withstood Michigan State’s defense, completed 14 of his 32 passes for 178 yards and scored two touchdowns for Notre Dame.
abstract: Notre Dame defeats Michigan State, 20-3, in college football.
lead_paragraph: In his third career start, Everett Golson withstood Michigan State’s defense, completed 14 of his 32 passes for 178 yards and scored two touchdowns for Notre Dame.

headline.seo: Notre Dame Snaps Michigan State’s Home-Game Win Streak
headline.main: Notre Dame Makes a Statement by Stuffing Michigan State
